<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM9.2.7">
<l>vārā yuṉṟiru pāta malarkkīḻ</l>
<l>pērā tēnāṉ vantaṭai yumpaṭi</l>
<l>tārātā yuṉṉai yeṉṉuḷ vaippileṉṟu</l>
<l>mārātā yeṉak keṉṟumek kālē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come, you who do do not give [me] a way to come close</l>
<l>without separating under you sacred foot blossoms,</l>
<l>you who, if I put you into my heart always,</l>
<l>do not satiate me always at any time.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
